title: International court to probe Duterte's drug war
text:
International court to probe Duterte's drug war Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:05 
The International Criminal Court (ICC) has told the Philippines that it has begun a preliminary examination of a complaint accusing President Rodrigo Duterte of crimes against humanity. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
